<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id795a796e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s1646"><num value="1646">§ 1646.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated annually such sums as may be needed to implement this subchapter. Funds appropriated under this subchapter shall remain available until expended.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id795a796f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/307/s7">Pub. L. 95–307, § 7</ref>, <date date="1978-06-30">June 30, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/356">92 Stat. 356</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
